WorldCom gains control of Digex, a hot firm specializing in Web
hosting for big companies. Control of Digex comes through 6 billion
purchase of Intermedia, which offers telecom services in a number
of cities, including Atlanta. (Kanell, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution)
