<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-09-05 17:17 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1907 &Cx1f; taf-z
u d BC-FOOD-NETWORK-2TAKES-N     09-05 1405
