SAN FRANCISCO _  FALL MENUS  _ As the days shorten and the air
starts to take on a sharp edge, stoves all over the Bay Area come
to life. &HT;    Fall is the perfect time of year to entertain guests. With that
in mind, we've asked two great cooks to produce a menu to suit
various lifestyles of Bay Area readers.
 &HT;     Intro by Michael Bauer  
 c. 2000 The San Francisco Chronicle  
