<P>
   The world has literally converged on Manhattan this week where
more than 150 world leaders and heads of state are arriving for the
United Nations Millennium Summit.
</P>
<P>
   The following photos have moved with stories on this week's
summit. Additional photos involving security preparations will move
as available this evening.
</P>
