child labor. Preserving a healthy planet. All sound like political
promises made by candidates. But they are also subjects touched
upon in the first national campaign for Stonyfield Farm. Yes,
that's right, the company that sells yogurt. In this print
campaign, there will be no beauty shots of delectable yogurt
dripping off a spoon or any boasting about the brand's tasty
flavors. Instead, the campaign takes on a more serious tone and
centers on celebrities who are advocates for the environment or
other causes. By Courtney Kane.
