<HEADLINE>
BUSINESS TRAVEL: AIRLINES FETE BUSINESS FLIERS WITH WINE 
</HEADLINE>
   (duplication notice: also sent with `f' code)  
 By JOE SHARKEY   
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   You probably don't want to be reading this if, like so many
